 age|df=yes|1997|9|8}}\n| birth_place         = [[Plovdiv]], [[Bulgaria]]\n| height              = {{height|m=1.72}}\n| position            = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub         = \n| clubnumber          = \n| youthyears1         =\n| youthclubs1         = [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]]\n| years1              = 2014 | clubs1 = [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]] | caps1 = 2 | goals1 = 0\n| nationalyears1      = |nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = \n| club-update         = 17 July 2014\n| nationalteam-update =\n}}\n\n'''Stoyan Grigorov''' ({{lang-bg|\u0421\u0442\u043e\u044f\u043d \u0413\u0440\u0438\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0432}}; born 8 September 1997) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Footballdatabase.eu|title=Stoyan Grigorov Facts|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.stoyan.grigorov.216871.en.html|accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|stoyan-grigorov/322629}}\n*[http://www.lportala.net/players/847.html Profile] at lportala.net\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Grigorov, Stoyan}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n[[Category:PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Bulgarian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Bulgarian footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stoyan_Grigorov"}
