 Vasilev\n | birth_date           = {{birth date and age|df=yes|2001|5|16}}\n | birth_place          = [[Plovdiv]], [[Bulgaria]]\n | height               = {{height|m=1.87|precision=0}}\n | position             = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n | currentclub = [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]]\n | clubnumber = 27\n | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]]\n | years1 = 2018\u2013 | clubs1 = [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]] | caps1 = 3 | goals1 = 1\n | nationalyears1 = 2017\u2013\n | nationalteam1  = [[Bulgaria national under-17 football team|Bulgaria U17]]\n | nationalcaps1  = 5\n | nationalgoals1 = 0\n | pcupdate = {{date|2019-6-1}}\n | ntupdate = {{date|2017-12-12}}\n}}\n\n'''Ivan Vasilev''' ({{lang-bg|\u0418\u0432\u0430\u043d \u0412\u0430\u0441\u0438\u043b\u0435\u0432}}; born 16 May 2001) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=botevplovdiv.bg|title=Ivan Vasilev|url=https://botevplovdiv.bg/profile/232}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|ivan-vasilev/488268}}\n\n{{PFC Botev Plovdiv squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vasilev, Ivan}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:2001 births]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:Bulgaria youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:PFC Botev Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n{{Bulgaria-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Bulgarian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Bulgarian footballer born 2001\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Vasilev_(footballer,_born_2001)"}
{"title_page": "Georgi Gaydarov", "text_new": "{{short description|Bulgarian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Georgi Gaydarov\n| image =\n| fullname = Georgi Ivanov Gaydarov\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1984|12|10|df=yes}}\n| birth_place =[[Bulgaria]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.78}}\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1=\n| youthclubs1=\n| years1 = 2004\u20132006 | years2 = 2006\u20132009 | years3 = 2009\u20132012\n| clubs1 = [[PFC Rilski Sportist Samokov|Rilski Sportist]] | clubs2 = [[PFC Vidima-Rakovski Sevlievo|Vidima-Rakovski]] | clubs3 = [[FC Etar 1924 Veliko Tarnovo|Etar 1924]]\n| caps1 = 34 | goals1 = 0 | caps2 = 41 | goals2 = 1 | caps3 = 70 | goals3 = 0\n| nationalyears1=\n| nationalteam1=\n| nationalcaps1= | nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = 17 December 2012\n| ntupdate =\n}}\n\n'''Georgi Gaydarov''' ({{lang-bg|\u0413\u0435\u043e\u0440\u0433\u0438 \u0413\u0430\u0439\u0434\u0430\u0440\u043e\u0432}}; born 10 December 1984) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defender (association football)|defender]]. He played in the [[Bulgarian A PFG]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Footballdatabase.eu|title=Georgi Gaydarov Facts|url=http://footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.georgi.gajdarov.54183.en.html|accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|georgi-gaydarov/140634}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gaydarov, Georgi}}\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:PFC Vidima-Rakovski Sevlievo players]]\n[[Category:FC Etar 1924 Veliko Tarnovo players]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n{{Bulgaria-footy-defender-stub}}\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Georgi Gaydarov\n| image =\n| fullname = Georgi Ivanov Gaydarov\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1984|12|10|df